  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "姚刚",
        "杜明",
        "马青"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚、马青、杜明、二解差同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "弟兄催马往前进，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杜明 （同西皮摇板） 好似猛虎下山林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位贤弟，你我弟兄自离京都，行了许多日期，尚不知还有多远路。一路之上\n倒看了些山林美景。只是天气炎热，你我就此缓缓而行便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同西皮摇板） 三人加鞭往前闯，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马青、杜明、二解差同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姚霸林马上自参详：\n赤胆忠心保家邦。\n东挡西杀、南征北战、马不停蹄、昼夜杀砍，才得封了一字并肩王。\n谁人不知我姚刚。\n怒恼了豪杰剑劈老贼一命亡。\n因此发配在鬼神庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宛子城保定了殿下刘壮。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "姚刚→杜明",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "杜明→姚刚",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 2,
          "白": 1,
          "同白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.5,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板",
          "西皮流水板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "黄飞刚"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄飞刚上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来武艺高，杀人放火逞英豪。开座肉铺生意好，谁人不知黄一刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下黄飞刚，在这黄土岗上开了一座肉铺。所养之猪，俱叫这庄上的人供给喂\n养，按日轮派。如有一家供给不到，轻者是打，重者我就烧房。因此就将这庄\n名改作恶虎庄。这且不提。只因我二弟名叫飞龙，三弟名叫飞信，每日在外做\n些绿林的生意，现已去了多日，为何不见回来。待我上街上溜达溜达。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "群羊难惹出山虎，强龙不压地头蛇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄飞刚下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "内白": 1,
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "黄飞信",
        "黄飞龙"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄飞龙、黄飞信同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞龙、黄飞信",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄飞龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄飞信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，你我兄弟此番掠抢，无有什么上等的生意，天气炎热，你我暂且归家你\n看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥言之有理。就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄飞龙、黄飞信同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "黄飞信→黄飞龙",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "黄飞龙→黄飞信",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "同白": 1,
          "白": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘老汉",
        "姚刚",
        "姚恂",
        "杜明",
        "解差甲",
        "马青"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二解差、杜明、马青、姚刚同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此处有一小店，你我弟兄就在此地安歇了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公差，"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去打店。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n嘿！店家哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这儿可有干净的上房？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚、马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将马带进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上面乃是朝中三位王爷。只因犯罪，发配他乡。还不上前叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n三位王爷，小老儿不知呀，小老儿与三位王爷叩头了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三位王爷用些什么酒饭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天气炎热，我等俱不用酒。但不知你这里都有什么吃食？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启王爷：我们这里俱是些粗俗吃食，无非是豆腐菠菜、冬瓜青韭、芝麻酱拌豇\n豆、小米面窝窝头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好。这些俱好，与我多做。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位贤弟，你我一路行来，用的无非俱是这些东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "菜饭到。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同吃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，这些东西均不能下咽，你们这里可有什么汤汤水水？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这里有的是八啦米星疙瘩汤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位贤弟，你我在朝山珍海味俱已尝过，从未吃过什么八啦米星疙瘩汤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，你就与我快快地多做。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位贤弟，也不知什么叫做八啦米星疙瘩汤？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀三位王爷：这疙瘩汤吃不成了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因本地有一黄一刀，因我家未曾供给他家牲口，竟将疙瘩汤抢了去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，黄一刀，他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三位王爷稳坐在椅儿上，细听小老儿说端详：此地名叫作黄土岗，有一恶霸名\n叫黄飞刚。他二弟黄飞龙，三弟黄飞信，俱在外面掠抢。他在此地开了一座肉\n铺，所养的牲口，均叫各家替他喂养，有一家供给不到，这轻者是打——"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这重呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这重者定要烧房！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀呀呀呀呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚推翻桌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我上前去会他一会！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥，想我等皆因情性不好，打死人命，才落得发配充军。你我万万不可再闯\n祸了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是我这怒气难忍。\n店家，再与我做疙瘩汤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥，请到后面一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马青、杜明、姚刚同下。姚刚上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听店家之言，此地出此恶霸，叫我怎能吞吃得下。\n店家，店家快来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见王爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。我且问你，此处可有秤么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚恂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快去取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷，看这杆秤可能用得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得。只是一件，这秤锤太小了，你与我换一个大的来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有一个，未免太大了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，不大。我且问你，方才你说那黄一刀住在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就在这十字街前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我知道了。少时二位王爷要是问我，你就说我拉屎去啦。你回避了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘老汉下。姚刚下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
