    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "姚刚",
        "楞儿",
        "黄妻",
        "黄飞信",
        "黄飞刚",
        "黄飞龙"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄妻、黄飞刚同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霸占黄土岗，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻逞刚强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨夜三更时分，连得三梦，甚是不祥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知所作何梦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一梦，梦见三个大汉，来到我家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楞儿暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知吉凶如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是三财进门，要主发财。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不祥之兆。此乃是三煞临头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第二梦，梦见水罐子里头有许多苍蝇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是金银满贯，要主发财。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看怕是恶贯满盈啦吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别胡说啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第三梦，梦见大火把楼全烧啦。一会儿成了平地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这更是要发财啦！俗语说，火烧旺地嘛！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是的，不是的。我看怕是一败涂地吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲话少说，楞儿挂幌子，做买卖要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做买卖。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同上买肉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给你这一块，给你这一块，去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走呀！\n到啦，就是这儿。不错。\n来，与我拿肉来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大爷，你也是割肉的吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是买肉的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有多少，我就要多少。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了，好了，有了包圆儿的了。你看这两大块臀尖好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我上秤称称。不行，打不住秤锤，再去拿来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的是肉。你看这两个九子，好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么叫做九子？你说肘子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肘子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要真不会说，你是个王八蛋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肘子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这不结了吗。不行，还不够。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不够再有两个猪头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将就算够了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，你称的有多少斤？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不过是拉拉的四两！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么着？一杠子肉都拿了去，你说是四两？这我可是作不了主。\n我启禀大爷：今个来了一个黑大汉子来买肉，一杠子肉都给他啦，他说是只有\n拉拉的四两。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，一杠子肉，他说只算四两？待我去会他。\n我说那一汉子，我一杠子肉，你全拿了去，你怎么只算四两？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四两。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四两，就算他四两。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你结钱吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与我上了帐吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们不认识你，不能写帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一定要写帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大爷：他还要写帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，你还要写帐吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要写帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "楞儿你就与他写上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给你写上啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与我送了去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们铺子里没有人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你身后那一妇人，她是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楞儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是我们大奶奶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就叫她与我送了去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你真是太岁头上动土，你招打！\n（姚刚、黄飞刚同起打，楞儿持刀砍姚刚，姚刚夺刀砍楞儿肩膀，出彩，楞儿下。姚刚追下。黄飞龙、黄飞\n信同上，与黄飞刚相遇。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位兄弟，来得正好。适才来一黑大汉子，武艺高强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄飞龙、黄飞信",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打上前去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
