      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马青、杜明上。刘老汉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青、杜明",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，二王爷那里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘老汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才王爷与小人要了一杆小秤，拿了一个大秤锤，不知往哪里去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想是找那黄一刀去了。你我一同赶上前去。\n（黄飞刚、黄飞龙、黄飞信、楞儿、黄妻同上，姚刚上。姚刚、马青、杜明同打死黄飞龙、黄飞信、黄飞刚、\n楞儿、黄妻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚 （三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
